
## Usage

### Online Access

You can access a live version of the TaxApp API online at([URL](https://taxapiapp.onrender.com/auth)).

### Postman API Testing

You can use [Postman](https://www.postman.com/) to test the API using the provided collection:

[API Testing Collection](https://www.postman.com/research-geologist-79253613/workspace/new-work/request/28030473-c0257cae-0fce-41af-b630-5f256aa3108a)

The collection includes requests for:

- Registering an accountant
- Logging in to obtain an authentication token
- Logging tax transactions by authorized personnel
- Viewing all taxpayers
- Checking user-paid and unpaid taxes
- Checking all taxes for a specific user
- Making tax payments
- Retrieving all taxes for all taxpayers

#### Authentication

To access protected endpoints, include the `Authentication: token xyz` header in your Postman requests, replacing `xyz` with the actual authentication token obtained during login.

### Sample Test URL

You can obtain an authentication token by logging in at:

[Login URL](https://taxapiapp.onrender.com/auth/login?username=final%20test%20&password=test)

